<font color="#FF0000">NOT OVER YET</font><br>
<tt>Sat Jun 21 21:47:00 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
So this string ends with a yatta-yatta?  I don't think so!  This has been anb active site for almost 8 months now and with all the things that happen when it gets warm outside.  The site has slowed down.  Life does go on.  Kids out of school and vacations and grass-cutting and all those things that engage us after a cold and dreary winter.  <br>
However, the problems still exist and the concerns are still real.  The MIA/POW issue is still unresolved, vets still haven't come all the way home and Lord knows that we still seek Peace.  So, folks, &quot;It ain't over...Til it's over.&quot;
<p><code>-- cbotkins@visuallink.com  (Chet Botkins) </code><p>


